				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ {\mathrm{CI}}_{\mathrm{s}}=\sum \limits_{u={u}_1}^{u_{NC}}\sum \limits_{i={i}_1}^{i_N}\frac{U{R}_{ui}}{N} $$\end{document}CIs=∑u=u1uNC∑i=i1iNURuiN
